ound-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">甲方（委托方）：</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">身份证号码：</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">乙方（受托方）: 刘富容</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">丙方（担保方）：广东智卡车联网服务有限公司</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">鉴于：</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">甲方需购买________________的车辆（以下 简称“该车辆”），车架识别代码为_____________,； 因该车辆购买价格较高，甲方无法以自有资金完全购买，考虑与其他意欲购买该车辆的自然人或法人（与其他参与了购买该车辆的实际持有人合称为“合作人” ）共同出资购买、共同拥有该车辆。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">现甲、乙、丙三方经友好协商，达成以下协议，以供三方共同 遵守：</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">一、甲方委托的事项</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">委托乙方与该车辆的原权属人沟通购买该车辆，办理付款、缴税、产权登记等相关手续；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">委托乙方作为该车辆在车辆管理部门的名义登记人，代甲方持有该车辆的产权份额；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">委托乙方对该车辆进行一般清洗、管理，并代缴相关费用；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">委托乙方在成功购买该车辆后宣传并寻找有意向单独购买该车辆的优质客户，并引导客户看车等活动；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">5.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">根据甲方及合作人的决定处置该车辆，并将处置该车辆所得款项扣除相关费用后按甲方及合作人对该车辆所持有的份额比例分配。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">二、乙方的权利</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">根据该车辆的市场价格变化及政策调整，向甲方及合作人发起处置该车辆的提议；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">若发生影响该车辆权益的紧急事件，乙方有权作出有利于甲方及合作人权益的紧急处理；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">根据甲方及合作人对该车辆的处置决定，选择该车辆的优质买受候选人；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">乙方可在适当时候与甲方协商收购甲方对该车辆的占有份额；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">5.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">如甲方转让其对该车辆的占有份额的，在同等条件下，乙方享有优先购买权。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">三、乙方的义务</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">以有利于甲方及合作人的方式善意管理该车辆，不定期向甲方及合作人汇报委托事项的进展情况；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">成功购买该车辆后，不定期向甲方及合作人公布该车辆的产权状况、车辆状态；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">关注该车辆的市场价格变化、政策调整等信息，并出具报告，供甲方及合作人及时获知该车辆的相关信息，保障其合法权益 ；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">乙方应依甲方及合作人的决定处置该车辆，包括但不限于出售、出租、抵押、借用、装饰、改装等影响该车辆权益的行为；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">5.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">甲方转让其对该车辆所占有的份额时，乙方应协助办理相关手续。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">四、投票规则</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">乙方可根据该车辆的市场价值变化在广东智卡车联网服务有限公司旗下的“智卡众筹”（以下简称“智卡众筹”）发起处置该车辆的投票，甲方及合作人可在投票期间对投票事项进行投票表决。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">乙方将委托智卡众筹以本协议第七条所述的方式通知甲方及合作人参与投票，并告知投票事项、投票期间及未及时投票的后果 。若甲方在投票期间未进行任何投票活动的，则视为对投票事项内容的默认同意。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">投票按甲方及所有合作人达到总人数的_51%（包含本数）以上同意即视为投票事项通过。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">无论甲方及合作人以明示或者默认的形式做出的投票决定，都不可撤回或撤销，且为乙方执行投票决定的唯一指令，视为甲方自己真实的指令，甲方应对乙方忠实执行上述指令产生的任何结果承担责任。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">五、丙方的担保责任</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">丙方承诺并保证，在乙方出现下列情形时，对甲方造成的经济损失进行担保，担保数额以甲方参与购买该车辆投入的本金数额为限：</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom