:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">七、通知事项及方式</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">乙方将通过发送手机短信、个人电子邮件（以甲方在智卡众筹平台上注册时或更新时提供的信息为准）、智卡众筹平台站内信和网站公告四种方式将下列事项告知甲方：</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">（1）委托事项的进展情况；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">（2）对该车辆的维修、管理及代缴费用等情况 ；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">（3）车辆状况及价格变化、政策调整等信息的报告；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">（4）发生的紧急事件及处理情况；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-s