font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、委托乙方与该车辆的原权属人沟通购买该车辆，办理付款、缴税、产权登记等相关手续；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、委托乙方作为该车辆在车辆管理部门的名义登记人，代甲方持有该车辆的产权份额；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、委托乙方对该车辆进行一般清洗、管理，并代缴相关费用；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、委托乙方在成功购买该车辆后宣传并寻找有意向单独购买该车辆的优质客户，并引导客户看车等活动；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、根据甲方及合作人的决定处置该车辆，并将处置该车辆所得款项扣除相关费用后按甲方及合作人对该车辆所持有的份额比例分配。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">二、乙方的权利</span></b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、根据该车辆的市场价格变化及政策调整，向甲方及合作人发起处置该车辆的提议；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、若发生影响该车辆权益的紧急事件，乙方有权作出有利于甲方及合作人权益的紧急处理；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、根据甲方及合作人对该车辆的处置决定，选择该车辆的优质买受候选人；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、乙方可在适当时候与甲方协商收购甲方对该车辆的占有份额；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、如甲方转让其对该车辆的占有份额的，在同等条件下，乙方享有优先购买权。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">三、乙方的义务</span></b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、以有利于甲方及合作人的方式善意管理该车辆，不定期向甲方及合作人汇报委托事项的进展情况；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、成功购买该车辆后，不定期向甲方及合作人公布该车辆的产权状况、车辆状态；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、关注该车辆的市场价格变化、政策调整等信息，并出具报告，供甲方及合作人及时获知该车辆的相关信息，保障其合法权益 ；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、乙方应依甲方及合作人的决定处置该车辆，包括但不限于出售、出租、抵押、借用、装饰、改装等影响该车辆权益的行为；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、甲方转让其对该车辆所占有的份额时，乙方应协助办理相关手续。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">四、投票规则</span></b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、乙方可根据该车辆的市场价值变化在广东智卡车联网服务有限公司旗下的“智卡众筹”（以下简称“智卡众筹”）发起处置该车辆的投票，甲方及合作人可在投票期间对投票事项进行投票表决。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、乙方将委托智卡众筹以本协议第七条所述的方式通知甲方及合作人参与投票，并告知投票事项、投票期间及未及时投票的后果 。若甲方在投票期间未进行任何投票活动的，则视为对投票事项内容的默认同意。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、投票按甲方及所有合作人达到总人数的_51%（包含本数）以上同意即视为投票事项通过。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、无论甲方及合作人以明示或者默认的形式做出的投票决定，都不可撤回或撤销，且为乙方执行投票决定的唯一指令，视为甲方自己真实的指令，甲方应对乙方忠实执行上述指令产生的任何结果承担责任。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">五、丙方的担保责任</span></b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、丙方承诺并保证，在乙方出现下列情形时，对甲方造成的经济损失进行担保，担保数额以甲方参与购买该车辆投入的本金数额为限：</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">（1）乙方未按约定，擅自挪用甲方投入乙方在智卡众筹的关联账户用于购买该车辆的资金。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">（2）乙方未按约定将出售该车辆的款项扣除相 关费用后按甲方占有的份额比例划转至甲方在智卡众筹的关联账户。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">（3）其他乙方因违反国家法律、法规的规定而 导致被吊销营业执照或被追究刑事责任的情形。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、除本条第_1_款所述情形外，丙方不对甲方参与该项目的任何亏损和收益负责。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">六、费用</span></b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、甲方及合作人委托乙方购买的该车辆总价值为_____________元（大写元人民币），甲方购买所持有的份额 占该车辆总额的______%既为__________元；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、乙方收取________零元______作为管理费；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、乙方在代甲方购买、持有、管理及处置该车辆等过程中代缴的费用从处置该车辆所获得的款项中扣除；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、如甲方因处置该车辆获得的收益需缴纳相关税费（如有）的，由甲方自行承担，也可由乙方从款项中扣除。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、甲方委托乙方向智卡众筹支付___零元____作为平台服务费。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">七、通知事项及方式</span></b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、乙方将通过发送手机短信、个人电子邮件（以甲方在智卡众筹平台上注册时或更新时提供的信息为准）、智卡众筹平台站内信和网站公告四种方式将下列事项告知甲方：</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">（1）委托事项的进展情况；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">（2）对该车辆的维修、管理及代缴费用等情况 ；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">（3）车辆状况及价格变化、政策调整等信息的报告；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">（4）发生的紧急事件及处理情况；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">（5）需甲方及合作人投票决定的事项及投票结果；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:微软雅黑,sans-serif;\