d-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、根据甲方及合作人的决定处置该车辆，并将处置该车辆所得款项扣除相关费用后按甲方及合作人对该车辆所持有的份额比例分配。</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">二、乙方的权利</span></span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、根据该车辆的市场价格变化及政策调整，向甲方及合作人发起处置该车辆的提议；</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、若发生影响该车辆权益的紧急事件，乙方有权作出有利于甲方及合作人权益的紧急处理；</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、根据甲方及合作人对该车辆的处置决定，选择该车辆的优质买受候选人；</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、乙方可在适当时候与甲方协商收购甲方对该车辆的占有份额；</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、如甲方转让其对该车辆的占有份额的，在同等条件下，乙方享有优先购买权。</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">三、乙方的义务</span></span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、以有利于甲方及合作人的方式善意管理该车辆，不定期向甲方及合作人汇报委托事项的进展情况；</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、成功购买该车辆后，不定期向甲方及合作人公布该车辆的产权状况、车辆状态；</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、关注该车辆的市场价格变化、政策调整等信息，并出具报告，供甲方及合作人及时获知该车辆的相关信息，保障其合法权益 ；</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、乙方应依甲方及合作人的决定处置该车辆，包括但不限于出售、出租、抵押、借用、装饰、改装等影响该车辆权益的行为；</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、甲方转让其对该车辆所占有的份额时，乙方应协助办理相关手续。</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">四、投票规则</span></span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、乙方可根据该车辆的市场价值变化在广东智卡车联网服务有限公司旗下的“智卡众筹”（以下简称“智卡众筹”）发起处置该车辆的投票，甲方及合作人可在投票期间对投票事项进行投票表决。</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、乙方将委托智卡众筹以本协议第七条所述的方式通知甲方及合作人参与投票，并告知投票事项、投票期间及未及时投票的后果 。若甲方在投票期间未进行任何投票活动的，则视为对投票事项内容的默认同意。</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、投票按甲方及所有合作人达到总人数的_51%（包含本数）以上同意即视为投票事项通过。</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、无论甲方及合作人以明示或者默认的形式做出的投票决定，都不可撤回或撤销，且为乙方执行投票决定的唯一指令，视为甲方自己真实的指令，甲方应对乙方忠实执行上述指令产生的任何结果承担责任。</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">五、丙方的担保责任</span></span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、丙方承诺并保证，在乙方出现下列情形时，对甲方造成的经济损失进行担保，担保数额以甲方参与购买该车辆投入的本金数额为限：</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">（1）乙方未按约定，擅自挪用甲方投入乙方在智卡众筹的关联账户用于购买该车辆的资金。</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">（2）乙方未按约定将出售该车辆的款项扣除相 关费用后按甲方占有的份额比例划转至甲方在智卡众筹的关联账户。</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">（3）其他乙方因违反国家法律、法规的规定而 导致被吊销营业执照或被追究刑事责任的情形。</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、除本条第_1_款所述情形外，丙方不对甲方参与该项目的任何亏损和收益负责。</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">六、费用</span></span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、甲方及合作人委托乙方购买的该车辆总价值为_____________元（大写元人民币），甲方购买所持有的份额 占该车辆总额的______%既为__________元；</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、乙方收取________零元______作为管理费；</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、乙方在代甲方购买、持有、管理及处置该车辆等过程中代缴的费用从处置该车辆所获得的款项中扣除；</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;cursor:pointer;outline:none;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\">、如甲方因处置该车辆获得的收益需缴纳相关税费（如有）的，由甲方自行承担，也可由乙方从款项中扣除。</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0.0001pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a style=\"margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;c